metadata.description:
kindness
it's that simple

artwork by catswilleatyou. 

This is a VR painting portrait of Gary's smirk.
This is one of 555 editions created to celebrate VeeCon.

Token holders get access to additional content at 
https://cwey.link/VEEC

This was made in VR and contains AR.

This artwork was created in virtual reality using PaintingVR. The image also triggers an augmented reality experience viewable with the free Artivive app. The AR experience shows the process of the painting being created from the perspective of the VR headset.
metadata.name: just vee kind
